22:03.323 --> 22:05.564
-Jason!
GUARD 1: Freeze, vampire!

22:05.783 --> 22:07.239
JASON: Jessica!
GUARD 1: Stay where you are.

22:07.452 --> 22:08.567
Let's go.

22:09.829 --> 22:11.160
JASON:
Hey. Hey!

22:11.372 --> 22:13.158
-Stop. You can't take her.
GUARD 2: That's far enough.

22:13.374 --> 22:14.659
