22:15.502 --> 22:16.992
JESSICA:
Jason!

22:17.212 --> 22:19.794
-What did you do?
-I called the LAVTF on your vamp slut.

22:20.006 --> 22:22.998
-Say goodbye to her forever.
-Where are they taking her?

22:23.259 --> 22:27.002
My body is a temple and you have
