23:31.244 --> 23:32.404
[VAMPIRE 1 GRUNTS]

23:33.913 --> 23:35.778
[ERIC & VAMPIRE 2 SNARLING]

23:47.510 --> 23:48.590
[YELLS]

24:04.402 --> 24:05.517
[SCREAMS]

24:15.580 --> 24:17.241
[CHATTERING]

24:19.626 --> 24:21.617
[CHATTERING STOPS]

24:23.713 --> 24:25.669
Evening, fellas.

24:25.882 --> 24:29.045
I'm looking for a vampire by the name
of Pamela Swynford De Beaufort.

24:33.890 --> 24:37.724
