41:15.474 --> 41:18.341
-Good.
-Fuck you.

41:18.560 --> 41:22.519
Tell your parents about werewolves,
werewolves kill your parents. Simple aS that.

41:22.731 --> 41:24.972
NICOLE:
No, because my parents won't tell anyone.

41:25.192 --> 41:28.150
SAM: They will find them.
They're the best trackers around.

41:28.362 --> 41:31.229
Hey, Daddy Wolf. You got that ice?

41:31.448 --> 41:33.188
Yeah.

41:47.255 --> 41:48.381
I don't want mine.

41:50.717 --> 41:52.378
Cool it.

42:10.904 --> 42:12.769
What's wrong with you?

42:14.574 --> 42:16.610
She's all right.

42:17.202 --> 42:19.284
Thanks.

42:24.751 --> 42:27.037
I guess now you girls owe me.

42:29.339 --> 42:31.079
TARA:
Heh.

42:33.135 --> 42:35.376
Fuck this place.

42:38.515 --> 42:39.550
Tara.

42:41.309 --> 42:43.049
-I know her.
-Willa?

42:43.270 --> 42:44.885
GUARD:
Burrell's daughter is a VIP.

42:45.105 --> 42:47.391
Don't mix with you
gen pop vampers.

42:49.401 --> 42:51.266
Look at you, already making friends.

42:54.114 --> 42:55.524
I could be your friend too.

42:59.536 --> 43:01.948
I've made friends
with a bunch of She-vamps in here.

43:02.205 --> 43:05.163
Kind of like
"I scratch your back, you lick my balls."

43:06.626 --> 43:08.912
When my daddy finds out
what you just said to me--

43:09.129 --> 43:13.247
He put you here, so I wouldn't be holding my
breath he's gonna come save you, sweetheart.

43:14.676 --> 43:16.712
Welcome to vamp camp, Miss Burrell.

43:27.481 --> 43:29.767
SOOKIE [ON MESSAGE]:
Hey, this is Sookie. I'm not in right now.

43:29.983 --> 43:31.314
Please leave a message.

43:32.152 --> 43:34.268
Hey, Sook, listen, uh....

43:35.530 --> 43:39.148
