with Jessica and I got to go fix it.

43:40.118 --> 43:43.906
I got so bent out of shape
the last couple of days, hating on vampires.

43:44.206 --> 43:46.538
But that ain't who I am,
it ain't who I want to be.

43:46.750 --> 43:49.036
So I'm gonna make it right.

43:50.629 --> 43:52.335
You're in safe hands with Niall.

43:52.547 --> 43:54.083
I love you and I'll see you soon.

43:55.133 --> 43:56.634
Come on, Stackhouse.

44:04.684 --> 44:06.595
You can put that stuff right there.

44:08.230 --> 44:10.687
You sure you want to do this?

